{"tid":1370181,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗警署圍咗水馬","createTime":"2019-07-27T02:13:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T03:59:59.000Z","uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b7da9858033cf66f52fecda268b970e404d007a7","tid":1370181,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:13:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bjXdxkG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbjXdxkG.png&h=b3b69393&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nfrom yahoo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係過街老鼠"},{"pid":"5a30ea5d0c5374e8205b1b48a62d0b7d83e39b4e","tid":1370181,"uid":178013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:14:27.000Z","msg":"【警黑合作極醜惡】小妹整咗「元朗宣言亅，去元朗嘅全部同我入嚟!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1368803\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1368803</a>"},{"pid":"1e6dc6e322aba98817f5a3ae1d23ce251a49c7d8","tid":1370181,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:15:12.000Z","msg":"警方已對元朗的遊行申請發出反對通知，並提醒市民今日不要到元朗遊行，否則可能違法。警方同時因應區內可能出現的遊行加強戒備。工人凌晨2時許到元朗警署外放置多個大型水馬，以防示威者衝擊。<br />\n<br />\n元朗警署報案室、停車場出入口及警察已婚宿舍外圍都加設水馬，車輛出入口位置裝上活動閘門。而據報，警方今日在元朗區高調布防，準備2000至3000警力應對。<br />\n<br />\n另外，位於元朗青山公路、合益路和泰衡街的3間馬會投注站今日暫停服務，位於洪水橋的投注站提早於傍晚6時關閉。"},{"pid":"882da5e4bc35b113fa2e91b39d754797674d6d6b","tid":1370181,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:15:38.000Z","msg":"有冇圍住D村呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbb7a5e6bac7e57e830b9104d2d5e381d118399d","tid":1370181,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"b7da9858033cf66f52fecda268b970e404d007a7","tid":1370181,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:13:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bjXdxkG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbjXdxk